snippet.title: Latest On The Johnny Depp and Amber Heard Trial | This Morning
snippet.description:
Johnny Depp's explosive libel battle with The Sun has entered a third dramatic week - with ex-wife, Amber Heard set to return to the witness stand for a second day today. It follows her testimony yesterday - where she alleged Johnny Depp had accused her of having affairs with a string of Hollywood stars, as well as threatening to 'kill her' on multiple occasions. But what has the reaction been stateside? And what else can we expect to come from the trial? Sam Rubin is joining us with all the details.
Broadcast on 21/07/20
